      "text": "Albert, in a book  co-edited with Olarinde (Albert & Olarinde: ed, 2010) observes that the cause of farmer/herder conflict in Oke-Ogun was not just crop damage but that the politics of June 12, 1993 elections in Nigeria and the mismanagement of the different problems by the interest groups in the country contributed to the escalation of the conflict. "
