      "text": "In the course of interacting with farmers while doing research on this project, it was stated that government was not sincere about the implementation of the various measures proposed by the USAID/OTI intervention project. This was why the Peace Monitoring Group (PMG) put in place to manage conflicts between Fulani Herdsmen and farmers in Saki West Local Government area fizzled out."
